      • computeTargetHeartRateRange

        public java.lang.String computeTargetHeartRateRange()
        Returns a target heart rate range as a string, with the min and the max rates separated by a dash. Min and max rates should be integers (cast as needed). Target heart rate range is 50-85% of the maximum heart rate.
        Returns:
        target heart rate range
